href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"Summary","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Das&nbsp;<strong>HTML <code>&lt;object&gt;</code> Element</strong> (oder auch&nbsp;<em>HTML Embedded Object Element</em>) repräsentiert eine externe Resource die entweder als Bild, eingebetteter Browser Context oder eine Resource die von einem Plugin geöffnet wird.</p>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\" title=\"HTML/Content_categories\">Content categories</a></th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Flow content\">Flow content</a>; <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Phrasing content\">phrasing content</a>; <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#embedded_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Embedded content\">embedded content</a>, palpable content; Bei besitzen des Attributs <strong>usemap:&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#interactive_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Interactive content\">interactive content</a>; <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#form_listed\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Form listed\">listed</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#form_submittable\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Form submittable\">submittable</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#form-associated_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Form-associated content\">form-associated</a> element.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Erlaubter Inhalt</th>\n   <td>Null oder mehrere <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/param\"><code>&lt;param&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Elemente, dann&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#transparent_content_models\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Transparent content models\">Transparent content</a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Tag omission</th>\n   <td>Keine, sowohl das Anfangs- als auch das End-Tag sind erforderlich.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Permitted parent elements</th>\n   <td>Jedes Element das <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#embedded_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Embedded content\">embedded content</a>&nbsp;erlaubt.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">DOM interface</th>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLObjectElement\"><code>HTMLObjectElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attributes","title":"Attributes","isH3":false,"content":"<p><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">Dieses Element enthält die&nbsp;</span><a href=\"/en-US/docs/HTML/Global_attributes\" style=\"line-height: 21px;\" title=\"HTML/Global attributes\">global attributes</a><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">.</span></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"archive\"><a id=\"attr-archive\" href=\"#attr-archive\"><b><code>archive</code></b></a> <span class=\"badge inline html-version\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML\">HTML 4</a></span> only; <span title=\"\" class=\"notecard inline obsolete\">Veraltet seit <a href=\"/de/docs/HTML/HTML5\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">HTML5</a></span></dt>\n <dd>Eine durch Leerzeichen getrennte Liste von URIs für die Archive der Resourcen dieses <em>objects</em>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"border\"><a id=\"attr-border\" href=\"#attr-border\"><b><code>border</code></b></a> <span class=\"notecard inline deprecated\" title=\"\">Unerwünscht <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML\">HTML4.01</a></span>; <span title=\"\" class=\"notecard inline obsolete\">Veraltet seit <a href=\"/de/docs/HTML/HTML5\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">HTML5</a></span></dt>\n <dd>Rahmenbreite in Pixeln.</dd>\n <dt id=\"classid\"><a id=\"attr-classid\" href=\"#attr-classid\"><b><code>classid</code></b></a> <span class=\"badge inline html-version\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML\">HTML 4</a></span> only; <span title=\"\" class=\"notecard inline obsolete\">Veraltet seit <a href=\"/de/docs/HTML/HTML5\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">HTML5</a></span></dt>\n <dd>URI die Object implementiert. Kann mit oder anstatt des <strong>data</strong>&nbsp;Attributes benutzt werden.</dd>\n <dt id=\"codebase\"><a id=\"attr-codebase\" href=\"#attr-codebase\"><b><code>codebase</code></b></a> <span class=\"badge inline html-version\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML\">HTML 4</a></span> only; <span title=\"\" class=\"notecard inline obsolete\">Veraltet seit <a href=\"/de/docs/HTML/HTML5\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">HTML5</a></span></dt>\n <dd>Der Ursprungspfad zum auflösen der relativen URIs die durch <strong>classid</strong>, <strong>data</strong>, oder&nbsp;<strong>archive</strong>&nbsp;spezifiziert werden. Falls nicht spezifiziert, ist der Ursprungspfad der URI, document.</dd>\n <dt id=\"codetype\"><a id=\"attr-codetype\" href=\"#attr-codetype\"><b><code>codetype</code></b></a> <span class=\"badge inline html-version\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML\">HTML 4</a></span> only; <span title=\"\" class=\"notecard inline obsolete\">Veraltet seit <a href=\"/de/docs/HTML/HTML5\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">HTML5</a></span></dt>\n <dd>Inhaltstype der Daten die durch <strong>classid</strong>&nbsp;spezifiziert werden.</dd>\n <dt id=\"data\"><a id=\"attr-data\" href=\"#attr-data\"><b><code>data</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>Valide URL der Adressressource. Wenigstens eine muss für <strong>data</strong> und <strong>type</strong>&nbsp;angegeben werden.</dd>\n <dt id=\"declare\"><a id=\"attr-declare\" href=\"#attr-declare\"><b><code>declare</code></b></a> <span class=\"badge inline html-version\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML\">HTML 4</a></span> only; <span title=\"\" class=\"notecard inline obsolete\">Veraltet seit <a href=\"/de/docs/HTML/HTML5\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">HTML5</a></span></dt>\n <dd>Bei vorhanden sein dieses Boolschen Attributes, wird das Element lediglich deklariert. <em>Object </em>muss durch ein nachfolgendes&nbsp;<code>&lt;object&gt;</code>&nbsp;Element instanziiert werden. In HTML5, wiederholt sich &lt;object&gt; komplett sodass jede Resource wiederbenutzt wird.</dd>\n <dt id=\"form\"><a id=\"attr-form\" href=\"#attr-form\"><b><code>form</code></b></a> <span class=\"badge inline html-version\"><a href=\"/de/docs/HTML/HTML5\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">HTML5</a></span></dt>\n <dd>Das form Element, falls vorhanden, sodass das <em>object mit dieser Form identifiziert wird&nbsp;</em>(seinem <em>form Besitzer</em>). Der Wert muss eine ID eines <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Elements im selben <em>document</em> sein.</dd>\n <dt id=\"height\"><a id=\"attr-height\" href=\"#attr-height\"><b><code>height</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>Rahmenhöhe in Pixeln.</dd>\n <dt id=\"name\"><a id=\"attr-name\" href=\"#attr-name\"><b><code>name</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>Name des gültigen Browsing Contexts (HTML5), oder der Name oder Name der <em>control </em>(HTML 4).</dd>\n <dt id=\"standby\"><a id=\"attr-standby\" href=\"#attr-standby\"><b><code>standby</code></b></a> <span class=\"badge inline html-version\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML\">HTML 4</a></span> only; <span title=\"\" class=\"notecard inline obsolete\">Veraltet seit <a href=\"/de/docs/HTML/HTML5\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">HTML5</a></span></dt>\n <dd>Eine Nachricht die angezeigt wird, während die <em>object</em> Implementierung und Daten geladen werden.</dd>\n <dt id=\"tabindex\"><a id=\"attr-tabindex\" href=\"#attr-tabindex\"><b><code>tabindex</code></b></a> <span class=\"badge inline html-version\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML\">HTML 4</a></span> only; <span title=\"\" class=\"notecard inline obsolete\">Veraltet seit <a href=\"/de/docs/HTML/HTML5\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">HTML5</a></span></dt>\n <dd>Tabbing Position im aktuellen <em>document</em>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"type\"><a id=\"attr-type\" href=\"#attr-type\"><b><code>type</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/MIME_type\">content type</a>&nbsp;der Resource wie in <strong>data</strong>&nbsp;spezifiziert. Wenigsten ein <strong>data</strong>&nbsp;und <strong>type</strong> müssen definiert sein.</dd>\n <dt id=\"usemap\"><a id=\"attr-usemap\" href=\"#attr-usemap\"><b><code>usemap</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd><em>hash-name</em>&nbsp;Referenz zu einem <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/map\"><code>&lt;map&gt;</code></a> Element; d.h. ein '#' gefolgt der Value eines <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/map#attr-name\"><code>name</code></a> von einem map Element.</dd>\n <dt id=\"width\"><a id=\"attr-width\" href=\"#attr-width\"><b><code>width</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>Anzeigebreite in PixelnThe width of the display resource, in CSS pixels.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"flash_video_einbetten","title":"Flash Video einbetten","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Einbetten eines Flash Videos --&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>object</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">data</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>move.swf<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>application/x-shockwave-flash<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>object</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!--  Einbetten eines Flash Videos mit Parametern --&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>object</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">data</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>move.swf<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>application/x-shockwave-flash<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>param</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">name</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>foo<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>bar<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>object</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/the-iframe-element.html#the-object-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von '&lt;object&gt;' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/embedded-content-0.html#the-object-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von '&lt;object&gt;' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html401/struct/objects.html#h-13.3\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 4.01 Specification<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von '&lt;object&gt;' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Browser compatibility","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wir konvertieren die Kompatibilitätsdaten in ein maschinenlesbares JSON Format</a></strong>.\n            Diese Kompatibilitätstabelle liegt noch im alten Format vor,\n            denn die darin enthaltenen Daten wurden noch nicht konvertiert.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finde heraus wie du helfen kannst! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect2\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td>1.0 (1.7 oder früher)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td>1.0 (1.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/param\"><code>&lt;param&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Summary","id":"summary"},{"text":"Attributes","id":"attributes"},{"text":"Beispiele","id":"beispiele"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Das HTML <object> Element (oder auch HTML Embedded Object Element) repräsentiert eine externe Resource die entweder als Bild, eingebetteter Browser Context oder eine Resource die von einem Plugin geöffnet wird.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<object>: The External Object element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<object>","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<object>","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<object>: 外部オブジェクト要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<object>","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"<object>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/html/element/object","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/html/element/object/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: HyperText Markup Language"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Element"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/object","title":"<object>"}],"pageTitle":"<object> - HTML: HyperText Markup Language | MDN","noIndexing":false}}